<br>
But, currently, do wizards see any negative impact of the 63 fire pet casting Ice Comet, or feel such?<br>
From usage I find only way to make it worthwhile is to re-cast a new pet every 2 fights, as by then its OOM, and unless pulls are slow, takes too long to get mana back, even with /pet sit down and clarity. So no point buffing it and supplying it with summoned pet items.<br>
<br>
<br>
